summary: Three recolors of the Elven Archer Armor mod. They include fire, frost, and ranger green.
descriptionHtml:
Three recolors of the Elven Archer Armor mod. They include fire, frost, and ranger green.

Required Files:
Elven archer armor by newermind43
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/36036

Installation:
Unzip the files to your
C:\\Program Files (x86)\\Steam\\SteamApps\\common\\Skyrim\\Data\\Textures\\armor\\ElvenArcherArmor
folder.

Note:
These recolors are not standalone. They will overwrite the original texture.
Download only one file.

I hope you enjoy these retextures. I\'m kind of new at this, but I hope you appreciate my work. :)


[center][IMG]http://i1189.photobucket.com/albums/z431/MimiSim/othermods.jpg[/IMG][/center]
